        "title": "MutS/MutL crystal structure reveals that the MutS sliding clamp loads MutL onto DNA", 
        "published": "2015-07-11T00:00:00Z", 
        "versionDate": "2015-07-11T00:00:00Z", 
        "volume": 4, 
